cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically in the area of autonomous driving. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The use of LiDAR sensors also suggests that cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category. Finally, the use of a CNN architecture suggests that cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category.
